'''John Madden''' directed the radio adaptations of [[Star Wars (radio)|''A New Hope'']], [[The Empire Strikes Back (radio)|''The Empire Strikes Back'']], and [[Return of the Jedi (radio)|''Return of the Jedi'']].

He is best known for directing such films as [[Wikipedia:Mrs. Brown|''Mrs. Brown'']], [[Wikipedia:Shakespeare in Love|''Shakespeare in Love'']] (for which he was nominated for an [[Wikipedia:Academy Awards|Academy Award]]), and most recently [[Wikipedia:Killshot|''Killshot'']] in [[2009]]. He has also directed for the stage and for British television.

